33:58.312 --> 34:00.474
God is shepherding our church called Crossway.

34:00.575 --> 34:01.376
He is ahead of us.

34:02.117 --> 34:03.158
He's around us.

34:03.198 --> 34:03.899
He's in us.

34:03.939 --> 34:05.021
He's going to protect us.

34:05.061 --> 34:05.962
He's going to feed us.

34:06.643 --> 34:07.484
He's going to lead us.

34:07.824 --> 34:08.565
This is what he does.

34:09.366 --> 34:12.370
He'll never leave us alone, and he'll never let us down.

34:12.430 --> 34:19.480
It's a manifesto, Psalm 23, to be lived by in real time, experientially.

34:19.820 --> 34:21.042
There's only six verses.

34:21.890 --> 34:23.892
So I think we can memorize six verses.

34:24.353 --> 34:25.054
Wanna give it a try?

34:25.094 --> 34:27.757
Try to memorize Psalm 23.

34:28.057 --> 34:31.621
I want you to store it up for the storms that are gonna be coming in your life.

34:31.982 --> 34:32.462
Store it up.

34:33.143 --> 34:33.904
This is what you'll do.

34:34.985 --> 34:37.248
We will experience the Psalm like never before.

34:37.688 --> 34:38.329
So let's do this.

34:38.629 --> 34:40.631
Go back to Psalm 23 and I'll end with this.

34:41.793 --> 34:42.293
Psalm 23.

34:42.574 --> 34:45.277
I want us to read it out loud together.

34:45.898 --> 34:48.641
You're like, oh no, I didn't bring a Bible and I haven't memorized it.

34:48.781 --> 34:49.842
Dog on it.

34:53.570 --> 34:55.052
Psalm 23, ready, let's begin.

34:55.633 --> 34:57.937
The Lord is my shepherd, I shall not want.

34:58.538 --> 35:00.761
He makes me lie down in green pastures.

35:01.162 --> 35:03.245
He leads me beside still waters.

35:03.766 --> 35:05.148
He restores my soul.

35:05.809 --> 35:09.114
He leads me in paths of righteousness for his name's sake.

35:09.615 --> 35:13.681
And even though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death, I will fear no evil.

35:14.082 --> 35:15.124
For you are with me.

35:15.484 --> 35:17.848
Your rod and your staff, they comfort me.

35:18.409 --> 35:21.874
You prepare a table before me in the presence of my enemies.

35:21.986 --> 35:25.332
You anoint my head with oil, my cup overflows.

35:25.993 --> 35:33.185
Surely goodness and mercy shall follow me all the days of my life, and I shall dwell in the house of the Lord forever."

35:34.287 --> 35:34.848
Hallelujah.

35:34.868 --> 35:35.609
Lord, praise you.

35:36.391 --> 35:37.052
We thank you.

35:37.092 --> 35:40.317
Holy Spirit, we pray that you would give us.

35:41.099 --> 35:42.421
Unction, that you would give us.

35:43.583 --> 35:45.106
Eyes to see and ears to hear.

35:45.146 --> 35:47.730
We don't want to just put Psalm 23 in our brain.

35:48.034 --> 35:49.535
We want it to be in our life.

35:49.596 --> 35:50.376
We live this.

35:50.456 --> 35:51.537
You are our pastor.

35:51.898 --> 35:52.859
You shepherd us.

35:53.579 --> 35:54.981
This is who you are to us.

35:55.301 --> 36:01.467
And I pray, Lord, for a dear person in this room that might be feeling that they're a lost sheep, that they have wandered from the sheepfold.

36:02.268 --> 36:08.894
God, I pray then in the sound of my prayer right now that they would realize that you've always been at work, that you've always been with them.

36:09.475 --> 36:16.562
And so, God, I pray that you'd give them hope, give them peace, give them strength, helped them to realize that you're drawing them back to yourself.

36:17.058 --> 36:23.267
You are shepherding their life, even in the darkest moments that they have gone through, even when the lights were turned out.

36:23.287 --> 36:25.850
Somebody hit the switch and it's completely black.

36:26.391 --> 36:29.555
Help them to realize, Lord, that you have been shepherding them.

36:30.176 --> 36:31.198
This is who you are.

36:31.919 --> 36:32.880
You're their pastor.

36:34.082 --> 36:37.947
And so God help us to go through this series with your favor and your blessing.

36:38.628 --> 36:39.589
We want to learn more.

36:39.629 --> 36:40.751
Help us to memorize it.

36:42.253 --> 36:43.154
Help us to live it.

36:45.186 --> 36:46.728
In Jesus' name we all pray.

36:46.768 --> 36:46.949
Amen?

36:47.770 --> 37:06.258
God bless you.

